            </div>
            <div class="psws-status psws-st-red">
              <div class="psws-status-label">🔴 Paused</div>
              <div class="psws-status-val">Defer Ask</div>
              <div class="psws-status-desc">Score ≥60 or regulatory/legal flag. Ask deferred. File escalated to AVP + General Counsel. Cultivation continues; solicitation suspended indefinitely.</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="callout callout-cr" style="margin-top:18px;margin-bottom:0">
            <h4>What This Protects</h4>
            <p>Harvard's greatest philanthropic risk in a volatile geopolitical environment is not a failed solicitation – it is a successful one that subsequently requires a public gift return. The PSWS is Harvard's institutional immune system: invisible when functioning correctly, critical when it intervenes.</p>
          </div>

