  'cmd-ytd':{t:'FY2026 Command Center: YTD Total Raised',s:'What a new reader should understand first',b:`${statsHtml([['$1.42B','Actual/projected FY2026 total'],['+8.4%','Ahead of FY25 pace'],['Q4','Highest-risk, highest-opportunity close period']])}<p>This KPI answers: "Are we ahead or behind?" It combines booked gifts, signed pledges, and conservative projections. For leadership, it indicates whether presidential time should be deployed toward acceleration or risk recovery.</p>${mockNote()}`},
  'cmd-gifts':{t:'FY2026 Command Center: Gifts Processed',s:'Operational throughput and confidence in stewardship',b:`${statsHtml([['84.2K','Gifts processed'],['+11.3%','Volume growth vs FY25'],['96%','Same-day acknowledgement for 8-figure gifts']])}<p>This matters because a campaign can only scale if gift administration can book, receipt, acknowledge, and audit gifts quickly without stewardship errors.</p>`},
